{
  "stem": "12447.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, at that time, I didn't actually distinguish from one neighbor to the other because everybody seemed to be pleasant in a way.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't mingle too much with the neighbors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were actually-- there were two Jewish families in the entire building, which was a three-story building.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly how many occupants.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Our apartment was number 45 on third floor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I don't recall exactly how many tenants were, so there must have been quite a few tenants in that building.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The only two tenants that-- actually three tenants, neighbors, that I recall-- which I got to know them later on when the war broke out much better.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But at that time, before the war, I remember, especially next door, one next-door neighbor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "His name was Dombrowski-- Pietro Dombrowski.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This family had-- they had twin children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I believe they were about my age, maybe a year younger.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they-- the boy was kind of a weakling-- I considered him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We couldn't play with him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they didn't have much to do with my Gentile friends in the street.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would see him as a next-door neighbor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would come from school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we never really played together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I know my parents had quite a, a friendship with them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to invite them for, like, a gathering, coffee.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And occasionally, my mother would make some good pastry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[CRYING] They would-- she would bring it in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they would have coffee.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mother would make a, a good vishniak, which is wine and cherries-- and she would share it with them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that-- I knew them, at that point, just from being friendly to us, more than some other neighbors.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then we had another neighbor, which lived about four apartments farther.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
